╔═══════════════╗
║    baremacs   ║
╚═══════════════╝

A modular and reproducible GNU Emacs setup.

Builds on vanilla (pure) Emacs.
Assumes GNU Emacs 30.1 or higher.
Uses straight.el and use-package.
Implements Makefile to build native .eln files.
Implements a systemd service to invoke emacs daemon at boot.
Comes with some shell scripts to facilitate working with Emacs.